---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Me - HomeLab Blog">
	<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
		<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">About Me</h1>
		
		<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md">
			<div class="prose max-w-none">
				<p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-6">
					Welcome to my blog! I'm passionate about IT infrastructure, networking, and cybersecurity. 
					Through this platform, I share my experiences and knowledge gained from building and 
					maintaining my home lab environment.
				</p>

				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">My Expertise</h2>
				<ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-slate-600 mb-6">
					<li>Network Infrastructure Design</li>
					<li>Cybersecurity Best Practices</li>
					<li>System Administration</li>
					<li>Network Monitoring and Analysis</li>
				</ul>

				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">My Home Lab</h2>
				<p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-6">
					My home lab serves as a testing ground for various IT projects and security implementations. 
					It's where I experiment with new technologies and develop the practical skills I share on this blog.
				</p>

				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Get in Touch</h2>
				<p class="text-lg text-slate-600">
					Have questions about my setup or want to discuss IT and security topics? 
					Feel free to reach out through [Your preferred contact method].
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>